channel.title: 717 Anim & Gfx list
channel.description:
So I have a client with 717 anims and gfx in it. But my server is still using 377 anim and gfx IDs.. That means attacks, specials, and a lot more are incorrect, and look horrible or stupid. Ex: Here is my servers dagger attack anim: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/uaOKYYz.png[/img]
Doesn't look right, does it..
